crew.original_title: Turbo Charged Prelude to 2 Fast 2 Furious
crew.overview: Turbo-Charged Prelude is a 2003 short film, directed by Philip Atwell, featuring Paul Walker, reprising his role as Brian O'Conner, in a short series of sequences which bridge The Fast and The Furious with its first sequel, 2 Fast 2 Furious
crew.title: Turbo Charged Prelude to 2 Fast 2 Furious

crew.overview: Jules Walters' unhealthy obsession with vampires leads to his dismissal from school. But when he steals a bat from the local zoo, his obsession may lead to his demise.
crew.title: My Ambition
